{"tid":1833332,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦: 香港演藝文化界 有危機","createTime":"2020-01-21T23:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T13:33:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1138de3ae10f613e9ac1670037b182a9cc277d93","tid":1833332,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T23:10:05.000Z","msg":"西環=中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377632&amp;fbclid=IwAR0BVNVUoofNE0a_SCrELb4BcJ1PNZ0s2SkIEUCARvKZ1P8rBFfpMboCc-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377632%26fbclid%3DIwAR0BVNVUoofNE0a_SCrELb4BcJ1PNZ0s2SkIEUCARvKZ1P8rBFfpMboCc-k&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmB5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f972824c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377632%26fbclid%3DIwAR0BVNVUoofNE0a_SCrELb4BcJ1PNZ0s2SkIEUCARvKZ1P8rBFfpMboCc-k&h=dd7d9cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377632&amp;fbclid=IwAR0BVNVUoofNE0a_SCrELb4BcJ1PNZ0s2SkIEUCARvKZ1P8rBFfpMboCc-k</a><br />\n<br />\n西環定5界別為高危<br />\n9小時前<br />\n.....<br />\n<strong>《政情》打聽西環已通知社團友好，有五大功能界別議席有危機</strong>，以上提及的飲食界、批發及零售界以及<strong>體育演藝文化及出版界</strong>全部包括在內外，還有工程界、測量界、個人票的專業界別，也是有危機。<br />\n<br />\n預警是做了，但如何拆解，建制陣營其實沒甚大計，暫時只能做好協調，輸給選票，也不要輸給不團結。"},{"pid":"17e66dd4da6966f5d33f3c4c1c1338298216f8e7","tid":1833332,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T23:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693a29f4f6a0f1d38fadea966680a2e11b134cef","tid":1833332,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de49742a008d2c8e860e1a2fed1a8629d8f32d3","tid":1833332,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T13:33:3